# Finds all prime factors by repeatedly dividing by smallest possible divisor
#==============================================================================
# FUNCTION DEFINITION: 'prime_factors'
#------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Purpose: This line defines a reusable function named 'prime_factors'.
# In Python, functions are defined using the 'def' keyword followed by the function name.
